		 * PROBLEM: When resolveSessionKey throws SessionKeyNotFoundError, the code logs it and sets sessionKey to null,
		 *          which results in _errors being set on the instance.
		 *
		 * ============================================================================
		 *
		 * USAGE EXAMPLE WHERE BUG MANIFESTS:
		 *
		 * File: /app/src/mail/model/MailUtils.ts (line 397-408)
		 * =====================================================
